enemy if war was thrust on it.
</P>
<P>
He said Pakistan cannot remain a silent spectator over the "
inhuman and barbaric atrocities" being committed by the Indian
security forces in the southern part of Kashmir controlled by them.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, Sharif said Pakistan has always endeavored for a
peaceful settlement of the Kashmir issue. (Pakistan-Independence
Day)
</P>
<P>
