Symposium of Society of Chinese Bioscientists in America (SCBA)
opened here Saturday, drawing top Chinese bioscientists worldwide.
</P>
<P>
Organized by the SCBA and the Department of Biochemistry of the
Chinese University of Hong Kong, the symposium is held at a
particular point in time as Hong Kong is working towards the
promotion of innovation and technology, including biotechnology
and biomedical technology, to attract high value-added industries.
</P>
