research, hepatitis and hepatoma, vaccines, plant and marine
biology and biotechnology, genomic research and traditional
Chinese medicine.
</P>
<P>
The SCBA international symposia are a discussion forum held
biannually for bioscientists worldwide, alternating between North
America and Southeast Asia.
</P>
<P>
The symposia also serve to forge closer relations between
Chinese bioscientists all over the world as well as universities
and private research agencies such as pharmaceutical companies.
