<HEADLINE> Macao SAR Preparatory Committee Political Affairs Panel Meeting Closes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 14 (Xinhua) -- The 15th meeting of the
Political Affairs Panel under the Macao Special Administrative
Region (SAR) Preparatory Committee concluded here today.
</P>
<P>
The meeting studied the topic of interim establishment of the
Macao SAR government organizations, reached concensus on this
subject, and suggested it be submitted for deliberation and
approval at the 10th plenary session of the Macao SAR Preparatory
Committee, which falls August 28.
</P>
<P>
The participants also discussed concrete steps concerning the
transfer qualifications of the existing Macao elected legislative
council members as the first legislative council members of the
Macao SAR. 
