capital Amman.
</P>
<P>
The official opening of the 9th pan-Arab Games will open Sunday,
but the athletic events, which began on Wednesday, started earlier
to allow athletes to finish in time for the August 22-29 World
Athletics Championships in Seville, Spain.
</P>
